(45, 'Gift Card RM50', 'VOUCHER', 300, 7, , 'EXCLUSIVE ON REDEEMME PLATFORM\r\nPerfect gifts for your loved ones on special occasions.\r\nTerms and conditions apply.\r\nGift card value is currently available from RM100 denomination\r\nValid for 1 time use within 1 single transaction (non-reloadable)\r\n1 year validity from the date of purchase/upon card activation\r\nRedeemable at all Jaya Grocer in-store outlets only\r\nCorporate discount available for orders above RM10,000\r\nFirst come First serve basis\r\nExpired on end of 2024', 31);
