(46, 'Dell 64GB USB A/C Combo Flash Drive', 'ELECTRONIC', 300, 200, , 'The combo flash drive has a dual interface that works with both standard USB and USB Type C ports.\r\nIt\'s an ideal way to provide up to 64/128/256GB of extra space.\r\nTerms and conditions apply.\r\nLimited stocks\r\nNon refundable \r\nPossession of the item during shipment is not the responsible of any redeemMe groups if there\'s any \r\ndefect.', 30);
