(55, 'Grab Gift Card RM50', 'VOUCHER', 1200, 29, , 'Valid for use in Malaysia only. \r\nEach GrabGifts voucher is only applicable to one Grab service type (food, rides, mart, express) \r\nNot valid to use with other Grab promotions or offers. \r\nNon-refundable, non-transferable, and only valid until the date of expiry.\r\n Standard expiry for users (employees / receiver of GrabGifts) is 6 months, unless customized\r\nExpired on middle of 2024', 29);

